{"serial": "13038", "department_serial": 12, "code": "FR4067", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "French Cinema:History and Masterpieces", "ch": "法國電影：歷史與經典"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Hsu, Chi-Lin"], "ch": ["許綺玲"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "201"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "法國語文學系", "en": "Department of French"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 39, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "視覺文化向來為法國歷史文化發展中的強項，也經常成為法國社會上之重要論述與議論話題。法國在十九世紀末、二十世紀初更確立發明了電影技術，且開拓了電影的多元視觀、美學、理論，與社會的多重對話。本課程將(針對電影發明初期至1960年代)介紹這項法國的重要文化資產，其形成的歷史脈絡，電影之為一門藝術的發展歷程，以及主要的導演和作品賞析，期使學生透過電影，不只增強法語理解能力，也進一步認識法國二十世紀的社會文化，提昇美學賞析能力，並開展多元史觀。", "en": "“The visual culture is very important in the history of French civilization, and arise often social discussion. France is not only one of the principal inventors of the cinematography in the end of the19th century, but also the pioneer of a variety of essential theories, debates, and aesthetics about this patrimony. In this course, we will present important directors and their film works from the beginning of the French cinematographic history till the 1960‘s, for the aim of improving French understanding and expression of students, as well as their capacity of aesthetic appreciation, and finally in order to open a wide and plural historical vision of world.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "順時代，以專題方式擇要介紹法國電影史代表性階段影作。早期默片中的紀實與奇幻、視覺形式動態藝術觀、二次大戰前的超現實主義、寫實劇情片、詩意表現主義，古典黃金時期，二戰時期的話劇電影、戰後的喜劇片、歌舞片、警匪片、作者論、新浪潮、短片風行期、人類學與歷史探索紀錄片等。\n視情況亦將安排戶外教學，或邀請學者專題演講。--至少安排16週課程 --同學須於課外時間自由參與指定的觀影活動\n(上課以中文講解為主 但使用全法文講義, PPT簡報和影片片段)", "en": "Chronic and thematic presentation of important directors and major films throughout different periods of stylistic evolution, such as silent movies in the early years, plastic forms, Dada and surrealism, poetic realism, classicism, theatre-film, literature adaptation, comics, music melodrama, Nouvelle Vague, documentaries, etc.\nOne scholar would be invited to give a lecture about a specific subject, and if possible, une activity out of campus will be organized."}, "textbook": {"ch": "“1.理論辭典 dictionnary－Aumont, Jacques et Marie Michel. Dictionnaire theorique et critique du cinema. Armand Colin, 2008.2.法國電影史　history of cinema－Jeancolas, Jean-Pierre. Histoire du cinema francais. Paris : Nathan, 1995.－Lanzoni, Remi Fournier. French Cinema From its beginning to the present. 2002.（《法國電影》。北京：商務印書館，2009。）3.電影分析的概論 analysis methodology－Fozza, J-Cl., Garat, A-M., Parfait, F.. Petite Fabrique de l’image, Magnard.－Jullier, Laurent et Michel Marie. Lire les images de cinema. Larousse 2007.（《閱讀電影影像》（喬儀蓁譯），台北市：積木文化，2010。）－Gaudreault, Andre et Francois Jost. Le Recit cinematographique. Paris : Nathan, 1990.（《什麼是電影敘事學》，北京：商務印書館，2007）－Mercado, Gustavo. 《鏡頭之後：電影攝影的張力、敘事與創意》。新北市：大家出版、遠足文化，2012。4.電影理論 theories－Casetti, Francesco. Les Theories du cinema depuis 1945. Paris : Nathan, 1999.－Aumont, Jacques et Marie Michel. L’Analyse des films. Paris : Nathan, 1988.《當代電影分析方法論》（吳珮慈譯），遠流電影館。－Stam, Robert.《電影理論解讀》（陳儒修、郭幼龍譯），遠流電影館。“", "en": "“1.dictionnary－Aumont, Jacques et Marie Michel. Dictionnaire theorique et critique du cinema. Armand Colin, 2008.\n2.history of cinema－Jeancolas, Jean-Pierre. Histoire du cinema francais. Paris : Nathan, 1995.－Lanzoni, Remi Fournier. French Cinema From its beginning to the present. 2002.（《法國電影》。北京：商務印書館，2009。）\n3. analysis methodology－Fozza, J-Cl., Garat, A-M., Parfait, F.. Petite Fabrique de l’image, Magnard.－Jullier, Laurent et Michel Marie. Lire les images de cinema. Larousse 2007.（《閱讀電影影像》（喬儀蓁譯），台北市：積木文化，2010。）－Gaudreault, Andre et Francois Jost. Le Récit cinematographique. Paris : Nathan, 1990.（《什麼是電影敘事學》，北京：商務印書館，2007）－Mercado, Gustavo. 《鏡頭之後：電影攝影的張力、敘事與創意》。新北市：大家出版、遠足文化，2012。4.電影理論 theories－Casetti, Francesco. Les Théories du cinéma depuis 1945. Paris : Nathan, 1999.－Aumont, Jacques et Marie Michel. L’Analyse des films. Paris : Nathan, 1988.《當代電影分析方法論》（吳珮慈譯），遠流電影館。－Stam, Robert.《電影理論解讀》（陳儒修、郭幼龍譯），遠流電影館。“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100%", "en": "100%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1.出席率與課堂討論，參與觀影活動的積極度。（10％）\n2.（講義）復習與書面專題作業表現（90％）\n--期中複習（35-40％）\n--演講回應單（0-5％）\n--期末評量（50％）“", "en": "“Evaluation of review  and a paper report 90 ％ \nEvaluation  of  the performance in the class and participation of film viewing 10 ％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週二9-10時；週三9-10/13-14時; 週五 13-14時", "en": "\"mardi 9h-10h, mercredi 9h-10h/13h-14h, vendredi 13h-14h\""}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "17+1", "en": "17+1"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "期末自主學習與評量", "en": "auto-instruction and evaluation"}, "domain": {"ch": "文化", "en": "文化"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "自學能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "多元文化觀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "審美欣賞", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "創意思考", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯批判", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Competence in linguistic expression", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance", "Self Assessment/ Peer Assessment"]}, {"competencies": "Autodi